# SECURITY STRATEGY:
# - Ignore actual .env and config files (contain credentials)
# - Keep template files (*.template, *.example) for multi-client setup
# - Ignore sensitive files like keystores and service account keys
# - Keep documentation and configuration templates
# =============================================================================

